to the world...

01:35:46.366 --> 01:35:51.455
for all United States citizens,
human and mutant alike‒

01:35:51.538 --> 01:35:53.999
Dr. Hank McCoy.
[Applause ]

01:35:55.959 --> 01:35:58.920
Way to go, furball.

01:35:59.004 --> 01:36:02.507
Thank you.
Thank you very much.

01:36:54.518 --> 01:36:57.103
